            <title>[LU-751] Kernel update [RHEL6.2 2.6.32-220.el6]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-751</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With the latest RHEL6 kernel from the 6.2beta release, the b1_8 branch fails to build with this error:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;make&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;3&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;: Entering directory `/usr/src/kernels/2.6.32-202.el6.x86_64&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
