cc1: warnings being treated as errors&lt;br/&gt;
/lustre/fs7/user/waschk/lustre-release/lustre/llite/super25.c:98: error: initialization from incompatible pointer type&lt;br/&gt;
make&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;6&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;: *** &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;/lustre/fs7/user/waschk/lustre-release/lustre/llite/super25.o&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Error 1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
